<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#2f2f4f">Originally posted by aanamdaru on 02-01-2002 11:21 AM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">Depends on the mood that I'm in when the person that wants the rez asks / if I know them / how they ask / how far I have to go.

If I see a corpse laying on the ground I'll /who corpse all try to click it to see if it's rezable then send them a tell asking if they want rezed (for free, unless they insist) or if I see someone looting their corpse I'll click them and continue running usually.

If a person gives me a tell and I'm not busy I'll rez them for free if it's in the same zone or if they provide transportation there / back unless the insist on payment, however I better get a thank you (only about 50% of the time /sigh)

If I have to zone for a tell from someone I don't know and no ride is provided and I don't know they person, I expect about 50 plat everytime I zone though I rarely ask for anything at all.

Aanamdaru I'Northa
Level 58 Cleric
Twilight Requiem
Druzzil-Ro Server

</TEXTAREA>
